<!--<h4>First Side.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>] śrīlōkē dharmā 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>dhyaṁ tē lōkāṁstāṁ praṇa 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>myahaṁ pālayē<unclear>ṁ</unclear>tastu 
<lb n="4"/>mā bhavaṁtu prithivī 
<lb n="5"/>śrī śakavaruṣamulu 12<unclear>23</unclear> 
<lb n="6"/>[ <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> plava] saṁvatsara kāttika <unclear>śu</unclear> 
<lb n="7"/><unclear>11</unclear> śukravāramuna śatabhi<unclear>ṣa</unclear> 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>munu AInanāṁḍu śrīmatu 
<lb n="9"/>kāmayabōyuṁḍu rājānugra 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>hamutōḍa mōṭṭupalli mala 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>maṁḍḍala perumāḷḷaku samā 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>rādhanaku Amudupaḍi cātupa 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ḷḷaku cedalavāḍastalamuna kanu 
<lb n="14" break="no"/>paṟiti kāmasamudramu kri 
<lb n="15" break="no"/>danu tirupaḍiyāramuku 
<lb n="16" break="no"/>gānu niccina varicēni maḍu 
<lb n="17" break="no"/>lu 2<unclear>0</unclear> maḍulu reṁḍunu 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Side.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="18"/>Ācaṁdrārkkamu rā 
<lb n="19" break="no"/>muḍu paḍiśēṣamugā 
<lb n="20" break="no"/>nu naḍapaṁgaladi rājyamu 
<lb n="21" break="no"/>nu dharmmamunu varddhiṁca 
<lb n="22"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> śrī 
</p>

